description: The Tropical Cyclone Storm Surge Probabilities data shows the probability, in percent, of a specified storm surge occurring during the forecast period indicated.  The product is based upon an ensemble of Sea, Lake, and Overland Surge from Hurricanes (SLOSH) model runs using the National Hurricane Center (NHC) official advisory and accounts for track, size, and intensity errors based on historical errors.
